{"id":5468,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/5468","type":2,"name":"剣勇伝説YAIBA","name_cn":"剑勇传说 铁刃","summary":"『YAIBA』は青山剛昌による少年漫画作品。1988年から1993年まで週刊少年サンデーで連載されていた。1993年、第38回小学館漫画賞児童部門受賞。また、1993年には『剣勇伝説YAIBA』としてアニメ化されたほか、同名でゲーム化もされている。\r\n\r\n铁刃是个以成为“日本第一武士”为梦想的少年，寄宿在峰道场。他与在学校剑道部遇到的鬼丸关系水火不容。但是，鬼丸被在家中地下找到的长眠的“风神之剑”所控制，心志受到了魔鬼的支配。与“风神之剑”相对的是“雷神之剑”。铁刃为了打倒鬼丸带着雷神剑出去修行。但是，雷神珠被抢走了。不过，如果能够得齐散布在全国的7颗神珠，就可以得到传说中的“龙神珠”。铁刃真的能打败鬼丸成为日本第一武士吗？-就是关于这个展开的故事。最后还有一个在鬼丸以外的新发展故事。从内容来讲是天真诙谐的少年漫画，但也正是这点十分有趣。\r\n","eps":[{"id":36878,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36878","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":2,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36879,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36879","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36880,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36880","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36881,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36881","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36882,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36882","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36883,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36883","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36884,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36884","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36885,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36885","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36886,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36886","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36887,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/36887","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":36888,"